{"tid":1716482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗回應甚麼是最大民憤時表示無民調在手","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:21:00.000Z","uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"85e2f2d3389bcb2dd6ffc5842f3e43ed9bba0da8","tid":1716482,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"13.11.2019 16:14<br />\n政務司長張建宗在立法會表示，社會的民憤是多方面存在，亦有深層次矛盾，可能修例事件挑動舊的民怨，例如房屋、就業、貧富懸殊等社會公義問題，都有機會引發風波，他承認有市民對警方執法有意見，但警方也有困難，當有治安問題，警方必定要回應，同時亦有市民埋怨暴亂持續，為何不可將暴徒繩之於法。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗被問到，是否知道社會目前最大的民憤是甚麼，他表示沒有民意調查在手中，如果議員有資料可以提供政府。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1210086&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1210086%26csid%3D261_341&d=eC9RRsiBNQJpYHZqEQI0QitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=0d1f7c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1210086&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"83196a230d435841d17328648c060533de407c45","tid":1716482,"uid":64694,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"都唔知畀咩反應好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班官而家連扮吓嘢都費事，成班都唔識轉彎，佢哋個腦係咪唔識轉，咩叫「無民調在手」，on撚99咁做乜柒啫，真係唔敢相信一個一個月拎三十幾萬人工嘅政務司司長居然喺呢個時候重可以講埋晒啲咁嘅嘢，無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3740c2ce2e621c0e6e33b09811bfdbfe199b4ca0","tid":1716482,"uid":255637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算啦 你估佢唔知咩 一路扮傻 想spin到自己唔關事之嗎"},{"pid":"9eba2e17c3b016c93291f166c5d9463bc4f3968e","tid":1716482,"uid":322796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"呢個基本問題都唔知就同我收爹啦仲出黎獻世"},{"pid":"5020350ccb22de55330f762